reviewText: The series really gives you a graphic look into the horrors of war.

What a terrible war, human life was so expendable...to the enemy to further their world domination and race extinction...and to America and her allies, extreme devastation for servicemen and their families. Only with a single minded effort, to thwart Hitler and his ilk, was the deaths of countless millions even tolerated.
This video, and others in the series, showed the raw guts of war, the determination of free men and oppressors alike, in the epic affairs of war.
